title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh, Hello - Havoc
description:
Oh, Hello, meet Havoc, an America rapper, record producer and one half of the hip-hop duo Mobb Deep. Havoc sits down with us to share the early years of his career and being in the studio as a young musician. 

Check out Havoc's new single "Tell Me To My Face" featuring Royce Da 5'9". The track "Tell Me To My Face" will be featured on his upcoming album release 13.
